WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.950
Hey, good morning, family. Praise the

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.190
Lord. Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:07.590
Well, that last video was over three

00:00:07.600 --> 00:00:09.509
hours long. I'll try to make

00:00:09.519 --> 00:00:11.990
this one not so long. Three hours. I

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.589
told Braden, I said that was a long live

00:00:13.599 --> 00:00:15.110
stream. I didn't realize how long I was

00:00:15.120 --> 00:00:17.029
